    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with precise turn-in, and the VANOS system has been recently serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. While it shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the subframe has been inspected and the rod bearings remain within spec. A mechanically sound, analog performance machine ready for the twisties.",
