    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition, perfectly balancing regular use with high-standard care. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014perfectly consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats show only light bolster wear and no cracks or tears. All power features, including the premium audio system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It boasts a comprehensive service history with recent fluid flushes, and the tires have significant tread remaining. It drives straight and true, providing a smooth, quiet ride with responsive braking. This is a reliable, honest vehicle that has been loved by its owner and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 35800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
